This script takes a POST request from stdin and returns a form with the action
set to the POST request's URL and hidden form fields for all of the parameters
in the body.

$ ruby xsrfify.rb -h
Usage: ./xsrfify.rb [options]
    -n, --newlines                   Use \n as line delimiter when parsing the POST request instead of \r\n
    -f, --full-page                  Print a full HTML page ready for XSRF instead of just the form
    -h, --help                       Show this help

